            <h2>Best Sales Engagement AI Tools for B2B Sales Teams</h2>
            <p>Sales engagement platforms are the operational backbone of modern B2B sales organizations. These tools orchestrate multi-channel outreach sequences across email, phone, LinkedIn, and chat -- giving reps a structured workflow to move prospects through the pipeline while giving managers visibility into activity metrics and sequence performance.</p>
            <p>SDR teams, account executives, and revenue operations leaders use sales engagement platforms to standardize outreach cadences, automate follow-ups, and track prospect interactions across every touchpoint. Based on aggregated review data from G2 and TrustRadius, the highest-rated platforms in this category combine sequence automation with AI-powered insights, built-in analytics, and deep CRM integrations that eliminate manual data entry.</p>
            <p>Key decision factors when selecting a sales engagement tool include multi-channel capabilities (email, phone, LinkedIn, chat, video), sequence builder flexibility and branching logic, AI features like send-time optimization and reply sentiment analysis, CRM integration depth (bi-directional sync with Salesforce, HubSpot), admin controls for team management and template governance, and total cost of ownership including seats, add-ons, and implementation. Enterprise teams need robust governance and compliance features, while mid-market organizations may prioritize faster deployment and intuitive UX.</p>
